ie went LD again (at this point you can assume he’s /q out of the game) he does not come back for the rest of the day. Later that night the jerk logs back in and transfers the items to one of his alts and starts selling off the items that DO NOT belong to him.<br>Now Hoile is not seen online for the next few days, and when he does come back he clams he’s been out of town. yet the moron has been posting on the guild web page over the past few days.<br>Now in the mean time his ex-friend and I have /peti a GM to look in to this matter and get his items back from him, after 3 days a GM shows up, his friend has to email Verant a list of items and what happened, after a week the GM comes back and says for the most part there is nothing that can be done because the asshole Holie says he gave the items to him.<br><br>So his friend is out about 350,000 plat in items. I personally contacted Holies guild Adamantine Kinship and told them what had happened, they instantly removed him from the guild, my warning to you all is to not deal with this piece of shit. If you see him needing a rez don’t rez him, if he needs anything don’t deal with him, don’t let him in to any of your guilds, he can not be trusted IMO he should be banned from EQ and I will not stop here on this matter I am going to bring this to the attention at the Fan Fair this weekend and push to have him removed from the game and have his friends items returned to him.<br><br>We are all at the mercy of our friends in the game when it comes to moving items between our players, Verant has not given us any other way to do it but to trust our best friends, when something happens like this to a player in the game by someone they called a friend online it just spits in the face of all that we can call decent.<br><br>I am asking that all of you when you logon the game after reading this to /peti and ask to have this scum bag removed from the game. None of us should have to deal with losers like him when we are onlin